## Monitoring (Delta Watcher)
- Satellite + ground sensors + admin feeds
- Multi-channel delta checks
- Alert → verify → enforce
## Market Layer
- NPV-based pricing
- Options / royalties / forwards
- Clear extraction trigger conditions
## Principles
- Value = certified resource × confidence × constraint
- Trust = repeatable verification over time

